.DT
set_stop_responding
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_stop_responding

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_stop_responding -  This method allows the toggling of the responses of the npc.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_stop_responding(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - 1 to make the npc not respond, 0 to make it respond again
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/response_mon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method allows the toggling of the responses of the npc.
If this is set to 1, then the npc will stop responding to
messages.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_stop_responding()

.EP

